            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "Among the huge amount of publications in the area we refer to the books [19,12,1] for the theory of age-structured systems, to [4,10,7,18] for optimal control theory of such systems, and to [2,8,9,3,15] for applications in some of the above mentioned areas.",
