                    "endOffset": 115093,
                    "startOffset": 115082
                }
            },
            "secId": "se0020",
            "sentence": "In order to give a precise meaning to equations (2)\u2013(5) (in line with, and partly repeating, the previous contributions, e.g. [19,4,1,10]) and the subsequent considerations, we introduce some notations, spaces and definitions.",
            "startOffset": 114956,
            "title": "Statement of the problem"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 113260,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "Nevertheless, mixed constraints are also important in the context of optimal control of age-structured systems.",
