            "title": "Boundedness of the Lagrange multipliers"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 113569,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "Second, mixed constraints can often be used for approximating problems with pure sate constraints.",
            "startOffset": 113471,
