                    "endOffset": 150529,
                    "startOffset": 150520
                }
            },
            "secId": "se0160",
            "sentence": "The advantage of vintage models in this context is their capability to regard embodied technological advancement (see e.g. [2,3,8,9] and the references therein).",
            "startOffset": 150397,
            "title": "An economic example"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 113333,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "First, often such constraints are meaningful in particular applications.",
