            "title": "Applying Theorem 2 to problem (1)\u2013(6)"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 113148,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "We stress that in the present paper we do not consider pure state constraints, rather, mixed control-state constraints; this is due to our assumption (assumption A below), which requires the control to be essentially present in the constraints (6).",
            "startOffset": 112900,
            "title": "Introduction"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 144241,
            "parents": [
                {
                    "id": "se0040",
                    "title": "Proof of Theorem 1"
                }
            ],
            "secId": "se0150",
