                }
            },
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "There are only a few known results: [7] (where the dynamic programming approach is employed), [14] (where only the end-state is constrained) and a few more in which the derivations are not sound.",
            "startOffset": 112705,
            "title": "Introduction"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 112057,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "The novelty is that the problem involves mixed control-state constraints.",
            "startOffset": 111984,
